description: Number of partitions of n into parts not of the form 19k, 19k+8 or 19k-8. Also number of partitions with at most 7 parts of size 1 and differences between parts at distance 8 are greater than 1.
references: G. E. Andrews, The Theory of Partitions, Addison-Wesley, 1976, p. 109.
